        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix: migrate watch app to single-target app",
        "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\n- Migrates the watch app from the deprecated WatchKit extension product to a single-target watchOS app.\r\n- Keeps the watch app bundle id and UI/runtime behavior unchanged.\r\n- Moves the existing watch Swift sources into the single watch app target.\r\n\r\n| before (Xcode 26) | after (Xcode 27) |\r\n| - | - |\r\n| <img width=\"416\" height=\"496\" alt=\"main-xcode26-watchkit-extension\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/bae1917d-17cf-42cb-b882-a13181d89210\" /> | <img width=\"416\" height=\"496\" alt=\"branch-xcode27-watch-single-target\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/504614a9-ab2c-4e57-b5e0-5aadc775b96c\" /> |\r\n\r\n## Verification\r\n\r\n- XcodeGen regenerated `apps/ios/OpenClaw.xcodeproj` from `apps/ios/project.yml`.\r\n- Xcode 27.0 beta (`27A5194q`) build succeeded for `OpenClawWatchApp` on watchOS 27 simulator.\r\n- Xcode 26.5 comparison was run from `main` against the original WatchKit extension target.\r\n\r\n## Real behavior proof\r\n\r\nBehavior addressed: Watch app still displays the same exec approval UI after migrating from WatchKit extension to single-target watchOS app.\r\n\r\nReal environment tested: `main` with Xcode 26.5 on iOS/watchOS 26.5, and this branch with Xcode 27.0 beta on iOS/watchOS 27.0.\r\n\r\nExact steps or command run after this patch: `DEVELOPER_DIR=/Applications/Xcode-27.0.0-beta.app/Contents/Developer xcodebuild -project apps/ios/OpenClaw.xcodeproj -scheme OpenClawWatchApp -destination 'platform=watchOS Simulator,id=82925FF5-D0F6-42AD-B6FB-7363A914F04C' build`\r\n\r\nEvidence after fix: Xcode 27 build log ended with `BUILD SUCCEEDED`; branch proof ran with only iOS 27/watchOS 27 simulators booted (`AECE7F8E-2E33-4DF5-B39C-06CB04B0C006`, `82925FF5-D0F6-42AD-B6FB-7363A914F04C`) and the iOS/watchOS 26.5 comparison devices shut down.\r\n\r\nObserved result after fix: The migrated single-target watch app showed the same exec approval screen as the main/Xcode 26 WatchKit extension baseline: `Exec approval`, `echo Apple Review Demo`, host `Apple Review Demo Gateway`, node `apple-review-demo`, agent `main`.\r\n\r\nWhat was not tested: Physical Apple Watch hardware.",
